1) Line up along wall 2) send friend to get beers 3) try not to spill beers as you stand shoulder to shoulder with other burger seekers 4) sit down (finally) 5) order bacon cheeseburger 6) ENJOY THE DELICIOUSNESS 7) get your ass up so other people can sit down Simple, solid burger that has remained pretty consistent over the years. Not exactly a relaxing dining experience - especially if you go in the evenings.
